{{Infobox dungeon |name = Weather Institute |image = [[File:Weather Institute.png|300px]] |caption = A map of Weather Institute. |tokens = 26,000 |location = Route 119 }} '''Weather Institute''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Hoenn]]. It has 49 tiles arranged in a 7x7 square, including 7 chest tiles, 17 non-boss encounter tiles, and 1 boss encounter tile.
